*IDENT NCC1TL  KEJ.
*/
*/ THIS MODSET UPDATES 1TL TO BE COMPATIBLE WITH DTCYBER
*/ AND THE TK4- CONFIGURATION OF MVS/JES2 RUNNING ON THE
*/ HERCULES IBM 360/370 SIMULATOR.
*/
*/
*DECK 1TL 
*/
*/ INCREASE MAXIMUM MESSAGE SIZE TO ACCOUNT FOR MESSAGES
*/ LARGER THAN 400 BYTES SENT BY THE TK4- CONFIGURATION OF
*/ MVS/JES2.
*/
*D 586  
 MGSZ     EQU    520D        MAXIMUM MESSAGE SIZE 
*/
*/ DISABLE CRC VALIDATION AS IT IS NOT NEEDED IN A TYPICAL
*/ DTCYBER/HERCULES ENVIRONMENT WHERE HASP/BSC RUNS OVER A
*/ RELIABLE NETWORK TRANSPORT (I.E., TCP/IP).
*/
*D 602  
 DBCC     EQU    0           DISABLE RECEIVE *CRC* VALIDATION 
*/
*/ GENERICIZE REMOTE TERMINAL NAME ("REMOTE01"), HOST NAME,
*/ AND NAME OF THE SPOOLING SOFTWARE.
*/
*D TLFSU1.1,TLFSU1.3  
 RTID     MICRO  1,3,/01 /   REMOTE TERMINAL ID 
 IBMH     MICRO  1,4,/HOST/  HASP HOST NAME 
 IBMS     MICRO  1,4,/HASP/  REMOTE SPOOLING SOFTWARE 
*/
*/ ENABLE CONSOLE OUTPUT STREAM IN SIGNON MESSAGE.
*/
*D 3154
          HEXO   CF,DATA     FCS2
*/
*/ MAKE 1TL RECOGNIZE "/*EOR" AS END OF RECORD INDICATOR IN
*/ PUNCH STREAMS.
*/
*D 4213
          PJN    PTS10.1     IF WORD BOUNDARY
*I 4215

 PTS10.1  LDD    RM
          LPN    MPUD
          ZJN    PTS11       IF NOT PUNCH STREAM
          LDM    1,EP
          LMC    2R/*
          NJN    PTS11       IF CURRENT LINE IS NOT /*EOR
          LDM    2,EP
          LMC    2REO
          NJN    PTS11       IF CURRENT LINE IS NOT /*EOR
          LDM    3,EP
          LMC    2RR
          ZJN    PTS10.2     IF CURRENT LINE IS /*EOR
          LMC    2RR &2RR:
          NJN    PTS11       IF CURRENT LINE IS NOT /*EOR
 PTS10.2  AOM    WEOR
          LDD    EP          SET NEXT BUFFER STORE ADDRESS
          ADN    1
          STD    BS
          LDC    PRC         SET PROCESS RCB
          STM    ETDA
          UJN    PTS12
